{"tid":618585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔RIP〕《再見螢火蟲》導演 日本動畫大師高畑勳逝世","createTime":"2018-04-06T02:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T02:42:05.000Z","uid":109462,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"010b4a304d11ef1646b0ac76a266004eed0eb67f","tid":618585,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180406/large/1522977962_09be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180406%2Flarge%2F1522977962_09be.jpg&h=54732f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾以《再見螢火蟲》感動全球的日本動畫大師高畑勳在日本東京逝世，終年82歲。<br />\n<br />\n日媒報導，高畑勳去年夏天開始身體變差，傳有心臟疾病，昨日在東京的醫院逝世。高畑勳1965年與宮崎駿及大塚康生合作，耗費3年執導出個人第一部劇院電影動畫《太陽王子》。1985年高畑勳、宮崎駿成立後來舉世聞名的「吉卜力工作室」。<br />\n<br />\n高畑勳最後一部作品，是花上8年時間炮製了新動畫《輝耀姬物語》，以水墨畫風格描繪出日本傳統故事。《輝耀姬》花上8年製作，2014年本報記者曾訪問他對作品的看法，被問到是否完美時，高畑導演指：「沒有作品是完美，我有時會想，如果這樣拍就好了，但我不會考慮是否完美。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》資料室/台灣《自由時報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180406/58039370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58039370&d=BqGjCycW4fN3prVCEleS%2FgHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=964fb5f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58039370&h=01803d27\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180406/58039370</a>"},{"pid":"1b6506483dfd4322dae40156ce6364cf6ac906d4","tid":618585,"uid":39413,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:41:13.000Z","msg":"Rip 童年陰影大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ed525abf50a424cf0789ae314ce32fafbe28af","tid":618585,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:46:45.000Z","msg":"rip唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif